  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18f7107e-094a-4dc6-b660-aaf77e5ada69\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:2px 0px 0px 2px;border-color:#004e82;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 255.0px; border-style:solid;border-width:0px 2px 2px 0px;border-color:#004e82; background-color: #004e82;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a112e30-7939-47ae-80d2-1815380ae2bf\" style=\"line-height:2.3;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-fae133bd-de90-411c-bdc8-d4c914e2efe4\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Promotional materials for the Event</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a7c955e5-07d9-4dcc-a08f-950108436d1b\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-089c23ae-3a1e-4c36-97b6-c2aa16b3cfac\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><b> :::</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-afe2049f-b450-4a07-9e38-e33fe2b9045a\" style=\"line-height:1.6;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3286f441-c0be-42a4-979f-007cbda8611a\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><b>행사 홍보물의</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-6cfa04d7-c908-4df3-8da3-bdc813eae48c\" style=\"line-height:1.6;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b8eface8-3f0a-4ed9-aa57-31400848d8f6\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><b>모든 것 (연속기획)</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb8a5f98-57c1-42b5-83c5-677b09100d4b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-643c6191-8171-4801-806d-48537f87b80a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8a2c4e94-9019-40f8-8f24-98dc2ba2e09e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">행사는 보통 행사 기획 대행사가 주관을 하는 경우가 많습니다. 그 대행사의 부수적인 파트로 인쇄 제작사가 서퍼트를 하는 형태입니다. 행사 기획 회사는 행사의 전체적인 업무를 주관하고 심지어 마케팅 업무까지를 대행하는 경우도 많습니다. 이 행사의 후원이나 지원, 진행은 물론 MC, 이벤트, 프로그램까지를 모두 총괄하므로 실질적인 대행사로서의 역할을 맡습니다. 그 부수적인 업무의 하나로 홍보물이나 진행 인쇄물을 인쇄업체가 담당하는 시스템입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9e265f92-b869-45c4-8e4f-7ca9d66d34d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-005c437b-8a75-4692-a684-5b5eb88a3ca4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dfc4d316-2c79-466a-880c-afc488d6be5e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5be4fe7e-c868-4586-ae47-822af06262db\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">행사 포스터, 초청장</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0637f2a4-9bb1-46a6-84b4-e305f70ea00a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6a8b9de5-f4c5-4b59-aa33-0fbb97194ebb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">안내 배너 및 현수막</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8d62e9f-3d00-4b63-b94e-07ddf96b4648\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e0683b60-2fb8-42f1-ac43-33b93ca0044d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">행사 티켓, 이벤트 쿠폰</span></p></li></ol><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-107762f9-06d3-4d3f-bb47-77c939993866\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-615bed59-2393-4ed9-b5d8-0d7d0b85dc9c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a722b14-715c-4866-b3fa-e138bb08d069\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7a510639-7265-4ebd-afcc-93d9f5eea431\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>4. 안내(진행) 팸플릿</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed12509d-7671-4886-84bf-4aef404c9961\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8db8d777-196d-4405-8564-d0cc6dc84aa2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>5. 홍보 책자</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6066aab4-724c-416c-bebd-c01189235501\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-02674d06-90aa-409e-a523-447396590d9f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>6. ppt 발표 문서</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebd682b3-2477-4a2d-9d13-2f9da0d92892\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-310669f5-2f5a-4ec9-a4ca-23b3562cb23d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>7. 이름표, 시상식 표창장, 상품권 등 이벤트 물품</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3043abef-cfeb-432e-b165-510fa41ef387\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-55a98169-e63c-4067-918b-48b927f13898\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>8. 안내 지역 폼보드, 약도, 공간 설명도</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f98e173-9243-4d5b-ac07-7aab23d2ce79\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b3f079fd-cc33-4f38-bf32-0fa812f8919e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>9. 기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4892c6b9-80c1-4aa2-a6cb-5a29598d2638\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9d87a1e2-ce50-4d27-81d7-75143f81b14c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b9ae9219-8b23-405c-b2cb-e6d9bea2a18a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-7722f85e-b7cd-48af-a234-3984151f9953\">\n<div c